data.description: This 3 bedroom brick ranch is spacious and ready for you.  Modern laminate flooring throughout the living room and hallways.  The primary bedroom has its own private half bath.  The kitchen opens up into the dining room and family room area.  Updates include:  Brand new breaker box December 2023, outdoor painting January 2024, newer roof, and newer water heater.  Large 2.5 car garage. There is a full sized shed perfect for additional storage, and a fenced yard.  All appliances convey including washer & dryer.  Enjoy the covered rear patio. All this home needs is YOU !
